Title: 继承
Describe: None
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
None

[Description]
如果一个角色或者用例继承于另一个，那么可以用 `<|--` 符号表示。

[UML]
@startuml
:Main Admin: as Admin
(Use the application) as (Use)

User <|-- Admin
(Start) <|-- (Use)

@enduml
------------------------------------------------------------
